'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #2210] on 1 June 2000 at 3:07:49 pm'!"Change Set:		104InfoStringMorph-smaDate:			1 June 2000Author:			Stefan Matthias AustA generalized form of ClockMorph (but without an option to switch off seconds).  It's quite handy for debugging or watching globals like VM Parameters. In a better world, this morph would also have a title."!StringMorph subclass: #InfoStringMorph	instanceVariableNames: 'stepTime block '	classVariableNames: ''	poolDictionaries: ''	category: 'Morphic-Demo'!!InfoStringMorph commentStamp: 'sma 6/1/2000 14:25' prior: 0!A generalization of the clock morphTry	InfoStringMorph new openInWorldor	(InfoStringMorph on: [Smalltalk vmParameterAt: 9])		stepTime: 50;		openInWorld!!InfoStringMorph methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'sma 6/1/2000 14:03'!initialize	super initialize.	stepTime _ 1000.	block _ [Time now]! !!InfoStringMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'sma 6/1/2000 14:06'!block	^ block! !!InfoStringMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'sma 6/1/2000 14:05'!block: aBlock	block _ aBlock! !!InfoStringMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'sma 6/1/2000 14:06'!stepTime: anInteger	stepTime _ anInteger! !!InfoStringMorph methodsFor: 'stepping' stamp: 'sma 6/1/2000 14:03'!step	self contents: block value asString! !!InfoStringMorph methodsFor: 'stepping' stamp: 'sma 6/1/2000 14:03'!stepTime	^ stepTime! !!InfoStringMorph class methodsFor: 'instance creation' stamp: 'sma 6/1/2000 14:07'!on: aBlock	^ self new block: aBlock! !!InfoStringMorph class reorganize!('instance creation' on:)!!InfoStringMorph reorganize!('initialization' initialize)('accessing' block block: stepTime:)('stepping' step stepTime)!